    "Ket"],
   Ket[<|$CellContext`S[1, Q3`$] -> 1, $CellContext`S[2, Q3`$] -> 
     0|>]]}]], "Output",
 CellLabel->"Out[130]=",
 CellID->44811593,ExpressionUUID->"0d74697a-99ed-4674-9f76-da77de59dca1"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[TextData[{
 "This gives the ",
 ButtonBox["Schmidt decomposition",
  BaseStyle->"Link",
  ButtonData->"paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/ref/SchmidtDecomposition"],
 " of the state. It turns out that its Schmidt rank is two and the state is \
an entangled state."
}], "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->1551193792,ExpressionUUID->"fd26e5c5-3ed7-4644-8d18-944d470735e8"],

