Cell["\<\
As purification is not unique, the above purification is not the same as the \
total state above. However, upon tracing out the environmental degrees of \
freedom, the purification reproduces the density operator.\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->194337718,ExpressionUUID->"59322b90-72eb-402d-8e6c-d8f123379bfb"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
